# kenopro79 Website Revamp — Design Recommendation

## What You've Got (and What's Worth Keeping)

Your site already has a **genuinely strong identity**. The Win95/98 OS-core aesthetic, the psychedelic animated splash, the door-open intro animation, the mist particles, the wood-textured "Enter Site" button — these are all charming and *very* you. The variety of metaphors per page (notepad, camera LCD screen, OS windows) keeps things surprising and fun to explore. Don't bulldoze any of that.

The goal here is to **sharpen and elevate** what already works, not replace it.

